# Intern Portal â€“ Round 1 Submission

A professional full-stack intern portal built with React and Express.

## ğŸš€ Features
- React + Tailwind frontend
- Express backend with dummy data
- Dashboard with intern data
- Static leaderboard (Bonus)
- Clean UI and modern design

## ğŸ§ª How to Run

### Frontend:
```bash
cd client
npm install
npm run dev
```

### Backend:
```bash
cd server
npm install
node app.js
```

## ğŸ“¡ API
GET `/api/intern` â€“ returns mock intern info

